strategies: the study had my full attention.
familiar: I tried to picture the place in real life and if I would like to be there or not. It helped me remember the images.
memorable: If I had seen or heard of places like the picture.
unique: If I had been to a place similar to the picture.
realistic: If I had seen it based on future vacation spots or vacation photos I've seen from others.
similar: If it could be somewhere that was a common place.
